  "prompt": "What are some good and romantic Malayalam songs?",
  "response": "Malayalam cinema has produced many romantic and melodious songs over the years. Here are some popular and romantic Malayalam songs that you might enjoy:\n\n1. **\"Mizhiyil Ninnum\"** - *Mayookham (2005)*\n   - Sung by K.J. Yesudas and K.S. Chithra, this song is a classic romantic melody that captures the essence of love beautifully.\n\n2. **\"Manassin Manichimmathile\"** - *Priyam (2000)*\n   - Sung by K.J. Yesudas and Sujatha Mohan, this song is known for its soothing melody and heartfelt lyrics.\n\n3. **\"Nee Harimaninnozhukum\"** - *Thooval Kottaram (1996)*\n   - Sung by K.J. Yesudas and Biju Narayanan, this song is a timeless romantic number that evokes deep emotions.\n\n4. **\"Arikil Onnu Vannal\"** - *Arabikadaloram (1995)*\n   - Sung by K.J. Yesudas and K.S. Chithra, this song is known for its romantic lyrics and melodious tune.\n\n5. **\"Mazhavil Kavadi\"** - *Aniyathipravu (1997)*\n   - Sung by M.G. Sreekumar and K.S. Chithra, this song is a romantic favorite that is often played at weddings and celebrations.\n\n6. **\"Oru Venal Puzhayil\"** - *Nirnayakam (2015)*\n   - Sung by Shreya Ghoshal, this song has a soothing and romantic feel, perfect for a quiet, intimate moment.\n\n7. **\"Ee Thanutha Veluppinteyum\"** - *Spirit (2012)*\n   - Sung by Sithara Krishnakumar, this song captures the essence of longing and love in a serene and melodious way.\n\n8. **\"Shivam Shivakaram\"** - *Bharatham (1991)*\n   - Sung by K.J. Yesudas, this song is an emotional and romantic number that showcases the beauty of classical music.\n\n9. **\"Poonkathe Poonkinaathe\"** - *Dhwani (1988)*\n   - Sung by K.J. Yesudas and K.S. Chithra, this song is a romantic classic that remains popular even today.\n\n10. **\"Manju Peyyanu\"** - *Diamond Necklace (2012)*\n    - Sung by K.J. Yesudas and Rajalakshmy, this song has a soothing and romantic melody that is perfect for a romantic evening.\n\nThese songs not only showcase the beauty of Malayalam music but also capture the essence of romance in their lyrics and melodies. Enjoy listening!",
